		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>St Thomas</placeName> <date>16 Feby 1853</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Revd Mr I Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">My Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">At length I have been able to succeed<lb/> through the Governments aid in inserting in the Congregation<lb/> to fulfill a duty so incumbent &#38; so much required<lb/> in the engaging a minister&#44; they have now agreed to have<lb/> one as you will find by reading the enclosed advertisement<lb/> which you are requested to have inserted in the Occident<lb/> for six months. I would also wish that you request the<lb/> Editor of the Jewish Chronicle &#38; archives Israelite to<lb/> do the same in their periodicals charging you with the<lb/> cost&#44; the whole expense to be repaid you by one as<lb/> soon as known&#44; please attend to this without delay as<lb/> every day is of importance to the congregation</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Altho&#39; the members of the congregation suspect<lb/> that I have been at the bottom &#38; that the governor has<lb/> been induced at my representation to act up to it still<lb/> I do not acknowledge it&#44; therefore beg that you will<lb/> not allude in any observation you may deem it advisable<lb/> to make to it.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The religious instruction to the children expressed<lb/> in the advertisement means the Sunday School&#44; he will<lb/> be permitted to keep a Hebrew &#38; English school also&#44; which<lb/> will bring in a good addition to his pay&#44; the laws give<lb/> him besides &#36;16 for any marriage &#38; 4&#36; for any one confirmed</p>
          <p rend="indent(8)">Believe me to be Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">yours truly</p>
          <p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">A. Wolff</persName></p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><addressee>Revd Mr I Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          
        </body>
